data.title: Debate on the Conclusion of the European Council: Statement by Margaret THATCHER, President in office of the EU Council and Prime Minister of the United Kingdom
data.meta_description: Official Visit of Margaret THATCHER, President in office of the EU Council and Prime Minister of the United Kingdom, to the European Parliament in Strasbourg - She particpates to the debate on the Conclusion of the European Council of London (5-6/12/1986). She is interrupted by Ian PAISLEY at the beginning of her intervention.
